name: Finnair A350 Business Class Los Angeles to Helsinki
description:
Watch this video to see the entire Finnair experience onboard their flagship Airbus A350 from Los Angeles to Helsinki.

In this video, you’ll see the Oneworld Lounge in Los Angeles and everything onboard, too! You’ll experience the Finnair A350 Business Class seat, the Finnair Business Class food, the Finnair Inflight Entertainment, and even the incredibly warm and friendly Finnair Business Class Service!

This flight lasted more than ten hours, which means you’ll see everything Finnair does on their long-haul business class flights.
